body:
Hi, my name is Duc, 20 years and from Germany. I am looking for a team as a Jungler and currently ranked in Dia 1.
I have experience in shotcalling and competitive online tournaments since I played in a high challenger team in Season 3.
Unfortunatly I had to take a break from Season 4 - Season 7 because of private reasons so I couldn't play the game activly and consistently, but since I'm at university now I want to try to go competitive again.

For more information add me ingame: uƒo
